column1:
'    # indirect offset
                ^\(
                (?P<base>&?0                  # just zero
                        |&?[1-9]{1,1}[0-9]* # decimal
                        |&?0[0-7]*          # octal
                        |&?0x[0-9A-F]+      # hex
                )
                (?P<type>
                        \.         # this dot might be alone
                        [BSL]? # one of this chars in either case
                )?
                (?P<sign>
                        [-+]{0,1}
                )?
                (?P<off>0              # just zero
                        |[1-9]{1,1}[0-9]*  # decimal
                        |0[0-7]*           # octal
                        |0x[0-9a-f]+       # hex
                )?
                \)$'
